OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with a little rain at times,
OL,7,Fespecially over the Southwest. Some
OL,8,Fdrier spells of weather too, with a
OL,9,Ffew clear interval in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,12,Frain at times, though parts of the
OL,13,Feast coast will stay dry. Some heavier
OL,14,Frain later in the evening, with strong
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
