OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FSunny
OL,6,Fintervals and blustery showers on
OL,7,FWednesday. Heavy rain and gales on
OL,8,FThursday, showery later. Colder with
OL,9,Fsunshine and showers on Friday, snow
OL,10,Fon hills.
